column5: I just pinned the spring fishing show seminar schedule and it looks like to me that half the presenters are board members....
Thanks for posting that TJ. I'll be going Sunday. Now I can plan my day. I better get there as soon as the door opens. I want to see "Big Jim's" muskie seminar. Thanks again.
I watched Gord Pyzer's musky seminar at the Odyssee a coupla years back and it was excellent, so I'll definetely be sitting in on his talk again this time too.  Well worth watching !!
yes it does TJ....and the rest will be soon as well they cant keep fighting it.....lol   theres more proof that OFC members are evrywhere....
Ya.. I don't want to miss Big Jim... and take in the musky semminars.... there chualked full of info....
